  <h2>üí¨ AI Customer Support</h2>

  <p>
    Traditional chatbots fail when customers ask questions outside predefined
    flows. AI Stack enables intelligent support that actually understands your
    product.
  </p>

  <h3>How It Works</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Ingest</strong> your documentation, FAQs, and support articles
    </li>
    <li><strong>Embed</strong> content into your vector database</li>
    <li>
      <strong>Query</strong> with semantic search to find relevant context
    </li>
    <li><strong>Generate</strong> accurate answers with citations</li>
  </ol>

  <CodeBlock
    code={`// Example: Support chatbot query
const response = await ai.chat({
  messages: [{ role: "user", content: "How do I reset my password?" }],
  context: await rag.search("password reset", { topK: 5 }),
  system: "You are a helpful support agent. Cite sources when answering."
});

// Response includes source citations
console.log(response.text);
console.log(response.sources); // ["docs/auth/password-reset.md"]`}
    lang="typescript"
  />

  <Callout type="tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Use the reranking feature to improve answer quality
      by 30-40% for complex queries.
    </p>
  </Callout>

  <hr />

  <h2>üìö Internal Knowledge Base</h2>

  <p>
    Large organizations lose productivity when employees can't find information.
    AI Stack powers searchable knowledge bases that understand natural language.
  </p>

  <h3>Ideal For</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>HR policy questions</li>
    <li>Engineering documentation</li>
    <li>Sales enablement materials</li>
    <li>Onboarding resources</li>
  </ul>

  <CodeBlock
    code={`// Ingest company documents
await rag.ingest({
  source: "confluence",
  spaces: ["Engineering", "HR", "Sales"],
  chunkSize: 512,
  overlap: 50,
});

// Natural language query
const result = await rag.query(
  "What's our policy on remote work?",
  { filters: { space: "HR" } }
);`}
    lang="typescript"
  />

